    "body": "`subset` takes the columns to apply it to. It looks like you're passing a DataFrame.\r\n\r\nAlso, `df.style.applymap(color_negative_red, subset = df.iloc[:, i])` is going to return a Styler, not a DataFrame, so I don't think your `while` loop is doing what you're hoping.\r\n\r\nYou might try making a smaller example and asking on StackOverflow, since I don't think there's a bug here."
